= SDL_SetClipboardText =
Use this function to put UTF-8 text into the clipboard.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_SetClipboardText(const char* text)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''text'''
|the desired text
|}

== Return Value ==
